				<td colspan="2"><span class="postbody">Okay i figured it out! just a straight hex hack. Got really lost before ( i mean come on, a 1.3gb file) but once i found my bearings it was easy.
<br />

<br />
 Find the texture number (hex) right under the ascii item description and just replace it with the texture number you want to appear. Probably do the same thing with meshes, once you find the mesh number.
<br />

<br />
Piece of cake!</span><span class="gensmall"></span></td>
